Dr. Elle Ramirez, Psy.D "QueenNoble" is an award winning international fine art artist, founder of QueenNoble Department Store, musician, author and a psychologist.  She travels and paints, creates exquisite artworks, unimaginable expressionism abstracts, rare mid century and modern design artistic wall decors and more.  One of her books is The Cart a true story novel.  Official website is [1]
